column23: cohort date is when newly hatched larvae were observed in the brood tank
site data would be reared at Lautan Production, Meze, France
I thought lat and long would be irrelevant in such a situation
Run and lane refer to the swimming chamber.  Not really necessary to include this info, mostly I have it there to help me get everything entered correctly.
The Fish ID is a combination of three things - the Australian Museum collection event number, the swim chamber run and the lane number.
